    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps identified at MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the package on the basis that the GCI study and experimental hemolysis comparison together provide sufficient confidence for the intended regulatory submission context. Monte Carlo UQ results demonstrate 95th-percentile nIH below the clinical threshold at all five operating points. Outstanding gaps in model form, model inputs, and test sample characterisation are acknowledged as epistemic limitations to be addressed in subsequent assessment cycles.",
